title: Former Catalan leader faces arrest in Finland
text:
Former Catalan leader faces arrest in Finland Saturday, March 24, 2018 - 01:22 
Former Catalan leader Carles Puigdemont faces arrest in Finland after authorities there received an international warrant for his detention issued by Spain, the latest legal action against separatist politicians from the wealthy northeastern region. ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
